posting_body: ['Sailhouse', '9740 NE 119th Way, Kirkland, WA, 98034', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 101', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'Welcome home to Sailhouse', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 986 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome home to Sailhouse Apartments!', 'Come join a Kirkland community devoted to nurturing your love of nature while simultaneously providing a remarkable array of metropolitan conveniences.', 'Our spacious and pet-friendly studio, one, two, and three-bedroom floor plans feature modern design elements and amenities.', 'Marvel at the sandy beach, boardwalk trails, fine dining, shopping, and nightlife options…all steps from your apartment!', 'Sailhouse represents the ideal backdrop for your life.', 'Pet Policy', 'Contact Leasing Agent', 'Office Hours:', 'Wednesday & Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Tuesday & Thursday 10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday & Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'V7UrGbkZ2Aw']
